Class DatabaseOpened

java.lang.Object
  com.cloudant.sync.notifications.DatabaseModified
      com.cloudant.sync.notifications.DatabaseOpened

public class DatabaseOpened
extends DatabaseModified

Event for database opened.

The event is only posted the first time a database is opened for a given DatastoreManager

When closed Database (by calling Datastore.close()) is opened again, the event is also fired.

This event is posted by openDatastore(String)
